SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID, P2.STORE, P2.PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT STORE1 AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE, PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT STORE2 AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE, PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT STORE3 AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE, PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID

(SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL ) UNION (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL ) UNION (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ) ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT ST.PRODUCT_ID, ST.STORE, ST.PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) AS ST WHERE ST.PRICE IS NOT NULL

(SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL) UNION ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL ) UNION ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ) ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) SUB WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, P1.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P1 WHERE P1.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P2.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, P2.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P2 WHERE P2.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P3.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, P3.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P3 WHERE P3.STORE3 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE1 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE2 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE3) S WHERE S.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS )SUB WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL

SELECT STO.PRODUCT_ID , STO.STORE, STO.PRICE FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) AS STO WHERE STO.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT TMP.* FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 ELSE NULL END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 ELSE NULL END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 ELSE NULL END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) AS TMP WHERE TMP.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS )T WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, S.STORE, S.PRICE FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) AS S WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, PP.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P JOIN PRODUCTS PP ON P.PRODUCT_ID=PP.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, PP.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P JOIN PRODUCTS PP ON P.PRODUCT_ID=PP.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, PP.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P JOIN PRODUCTS PP ON P.PRODUCT_ID=PP.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) AS A ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT T1.PRODUCT_ID, T1.STORE, T1.VALUE AS PRICE FROM( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 VALUE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 VALUE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 VALUE FROM PRODUCTS ) AS T1 WHERE T1.VALUE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 > 0 UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 > 0 UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 > 0 ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) PRODUCTS ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID ASC

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE ASC

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'STORE1 AS STORE',STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2', STORE2 FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3', STORE3 FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID, PRICE

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P1 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P2 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P3) AS SUB WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'STORE1 AS STORE' , STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'STORE2 AS STORE' , STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'STORE3 AS STORE' , STORE3 AS STORE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID ASC

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,STORE,PRICE FROM ((SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store1' AS STORE,STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) UNION (SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2' AS STORE,STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) UNION (SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3' AS STORE,STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS)) AS P WHERE P.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) AS ORDERS WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, P.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, P.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, P.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS TSTORE_1 WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS TSTORE_2 WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS TSTORE_3 WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) AS STORE_TEMP WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, X.* FROM PRODUCTS CROSS JOIN LATERAL( SELECT STORE1 , STORE1 UNION ALL SELECT STORE2 , STORE2 UNION ALL SELECT STORE3 , STORE3 ) AS X(STORE,PRICE) WHERE X.PRICE IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID, X.STORE

WITH S1 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL), S2 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL), S3 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) SELECT * FROM S1 UNION ALL SELECT *FROM S2 UNION ALL SELECT * FROM S3 ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT STORE1 AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE, PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT STORE2 AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE, PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT STORE3 AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE, PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID , CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 END AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 END AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 END AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS )X WHERE STORE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE

SELECT PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 END AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 END AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 END AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) TEMP WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) AS UNPIVOT ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE,STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE,STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE,STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY 1

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL), CTE2 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL), CTE3 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) SELECT * FROM CTE1 UNION ALL SELECT * FROM CTE2 UNION ALL SELECT * FROM CTE3

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID) AS TEMP WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE1 AS PRICE , 'store1' AS STORE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE2 AS PRICE , 'store2' AS STORE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE3 AS PRICE , 'store3' AS STORE FROM PRODUCTS ) T WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

WITH PRICE_TABLE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1'AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2'AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3'AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) SELECT * FROM PRICE_TABLE WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS )AS TOTAL WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID , 'STORE1 AS STORE', P.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P WHERE P.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID , 'STORE2 AS STORE', P.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P WHERE P.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID , 'STORE3 AS STORE', P.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P WHERE P.STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) AS TEMP WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE NOT STORE1 IS NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE NOT STORE2 IS NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE NOT STORE3 IS NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID, STORE

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) A WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

WITH T2 AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1'AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 ELSE NULL END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 ELSE NULL END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 ELSE NULL END AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) SELECT * FROM T2 WHERE STORE IS NOT NULL AND PRICE IS NOT NULL

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) SELECT * FROM T1 WHERE T1.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 != 'NULL' UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 != 'NULL' UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 != 'NULL'

WITH ALL_COMBOS AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM ALL_COMBOS WHERE NOT ISNULL(PRICE)

SELECT T.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, T.STORE AS STORE, T.PRICE AS PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1'AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2'AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3'AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ) AS T

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' STORE, STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' STORE, STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) T WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID ASC

SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, P2.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P1 JOIN PRODUCTS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P2.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, P2.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P1 JOIN PRODUCTS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P2.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, P2.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P1 JOIN PRODUCTS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P2.STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) ALL_ENTRIES WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1'AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE NOT STORE1 = 'NULL' UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2'AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE NOT STORE2 = 'NULL' UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3'AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE NOT STORE3 = 'NULL'

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL) RESULT ORDER BY RESULT.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCTS.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, PRODUCTS.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE PRODUCTS.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCTS.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, PRODUCTS.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE PRODUCTS.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCTS.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, PRODUCTS.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE PRODUCTS.STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT VIEW.PRODUCT_ID, VIEW.STORE, VIEW.PRICE FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) AS VIEW WHERE VIEW.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, STORE, PRICE FROM( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ) AS T

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' , STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3', STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) AS T WHERE T.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ((SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) UNION (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) UNION (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS)) PIVOT_LONGER WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT P2.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, P2.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P1 LEFT JOIN PRODUCTS AS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID AND P2.STORE1 WHERE P2.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P2.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, P2.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P1 LEFT JOIN PRODUCTS AS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P2.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P2.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, P2.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS AS P1 LEFT JOIN PRODUCTS AS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID AND P2.STORE3 WHERE P2.STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ( ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) UNION ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) UNION ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS ) ) AS T WHERE T.PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'STORE1 AS STORE',STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'STORE2 AS STORE',STORE2 AS STORE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'STORE3 AS STORE',STORE3 AS STORE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'store1' STORE , STORE1 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'store2' STORE , STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID , 'store3' STORE , STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 IS NOT NULL ) S

SELECT * FROM( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS) AS T1 WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store1' AS STORE,STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 > 0 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2' AS STORE,STORE2 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 > 0 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3 > 0 ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store1' AS STORE, STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE1 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store2' AS STORE, STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE2 UNION SELECT PRODUCT_ID,'store3' AS STORE, STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS WHERE STORE3

WITH CTE AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 END) AS STORE, MAX(CASE WHEN STORE1 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE1 END) AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 END) AS STORE, MAX(CASE WHEN STORE2 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE2 END) AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 END) AS STORE, MAX(CASE WHEN STORE3 IS NOT NULL THEN STORE3 END) AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS GROUP BY 1) SELECT PRODUCT_ID,STORE,PRICE FROM CTE WHERE PRICE IS NOT NULL

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store1' AS STORE, P2.STORE1 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P JOIN PRODUCTS P2 ON P.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID AND P2.STORE1 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store2' AS STORE, P2.STORE2 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P JOIN PRODUCTS P2 ON P.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID AND P2.STORE2 IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, 'store3' AS STORE, P2.STORE3 AS PRICE FROM PRODUCTS P JOIN PRODUCTS P2 ON P.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID AND P2.STORE3 IS NOT NULL
